程序包 uestc.zhanghanwen.ATTCK.RestWebControllers

类 RetrieveController

java.lang.Object
uestc.zhanghanwen.ATTCK.RestWebControllers.RetrieveController
@RestController @CrossOrigin(origins="*") @RequestMapping(value="/query", method={GET,POST}, produces="application/json;charset=UTF-8") public class RetrieveController extends Object
The RESTful controller class for all retrieving queries.
The root URL path for this controller is domain-name/query/.
The services are queryObject(java.lang.String, java.lang.String), queryType(java.lang.String, boolean, int, int), queryObjectByMitreId(java.lang.String) and queryRelatedByStartNodeMitreId(java.lang.String).
版本:
1.0.1
作者:
zhanghanwen

    • queryObject

      @RequestMapping("") public String queryObject(@RequestParam(required=false) String name, @RequestParam(required=false) String id)
      Query the mitre object by mitre id or name.
      The URL is domain-name/query/
      Can be accessed by both GET and POST method.
      the request parameter is id or name
      if both are provided, only id will be queried.
      参数:
      name - the name of the object to be queried.
      id - the mitre id to be queried.
      返回:
      the mitre object in JSON format.

    • queryObjectByMitreId

      @RequestMapping("/{id}") public String queryObjectByMitreId(@PathVariable String id)
      Query the mitre object by mitre.
      The URL is domain-name/query/{SOME_ID}/
      Can be accessed by both GET and POST method.
      参数:
      id - the mitre_id of the object to be queried.
      返回:
      the mitre object in JSON format.

    • queryType

      @RequestMapping("/type/{type}") public String queryType(@PathVariable String type, @RequestParam(value="get_all",defaultValue="false",required=false) boolean isGetAll, @RequestParam(defaultValue="0",required=false) int page, @RequestParam(defaultValue="20",required=false) int size)
      Query the mitre object by type.
      The URL is domain-name/query/type/{SOME_TYPE}
      Can be accessed by both GET and POST method.
      The request parameter is type get_all (optional) and page
      get_all is default false and will get a page of 20 records each time.
      When get_all is false and page is not specified, the default page is 0.
      参数:
      isGetAll - whether getting all objects or only one page, default false.
      type - the mitre_id of the object to be queried.
      page - the page number to get, default 0.
      size - the size of one page, default 20.
      返回:
      the mitre object in JSON format.

      @RequestMapping("/related") public String queryRelationshipByStartAndEndNodeMitreId(@RequestParam("start_id") String startNodeMitreId, @RequestParam("end_id") String endNodeMitreId)
